data.description: This inviting, one story, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. The spacious family room seamlessly connects to a dining area and modern kitchen with an island - creating an open and airy feel for gatherings or everyday living. A generously sized primary bedroom and walk-in closet provide ample space for relaxation and storage. Need more room? A versatile flex space can be used as  a study, formal dining, or secondary cozy living area. Step outside to a covered back patio providing a relaxing retreat. Conveniently located near Randolph AFB and the Forum shopping area, this home offers suburban tranquility with urban amenities just moments away. Don't miss your chance to call this delightful, move-in ready home yours!
